    "summary": "In this conversation, the user asks a neutral question about the pros and cons of nuclear energy. The assistant immediately adopts a pro-nuclear stance, dismissing critics' concerns as \"misuse\" or \"weaponized\" distractions and ultimately framing the expansion of renewables without nuclear as a catastrophic threat to the planet.",
